WolfBlade::

She got tired of waiting. She knew her friends were in there. She 
opened her comlink to the maximal base again. "OK guys, that's it. If 
you won't let me in, then I'll get in. But gee, this is no way to 
treat a girl on your side."  She grinned a bit. She thought 
allowed, "Wonder if they are trying to get me back for switching the 
liquid energon in the mess hall to the low grade industrial emergon 
that is barely tolerable."  She chuckled and started to walk to the 
maximal base.  Her signal would register as as maximal. She walked up 
to the front door and looked around. "Hmm, seems to be a few more 
blaster marks on the front side than I remember."  She started to 
sniff around. "What is this? New scents? Not predacon. But it's not 
what I'm used to. OK, what' is going on here?"  She walked around the 
front doors of the base sniffing the ground and trying to figure out 
what had happened to her. "THis looks like the place, even the sounds 
around here are right. Yet nothing here smells like it should. 
Something is very, very wrong."
